{"id":102078,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/断网了，你还能用电脑做什么？/","date":"2010-08-31T23:14:54Z","modified":"2010-08-31T23:14:54Z","title":"断网了，你还能用电脑做什么？","content":"<p><p>来自: <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/931251/2\">www.yeeyan.org &#8211; FeedzShare</a>  <br />\n<br />发布时间:2010年08月31日,  已有 5 人推荐 </p>\n<hr>\n<div>\n<p>原作者：<br />来源<a href=\"http://www.yeeyan.org/\">Other Ways to Use Your PC When Your Internet Dies</a><br />译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/90729\">royaso</a></p>\n<p><span></p>\n<h2><a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/26853/other-ways-to-use-your-pc-when-your-internet-dies/\">断网了，你还能用电脑做什么？</p>\n<div></div>\n<p> </a></h2>\n<div><span>作者：<span>Mysticgeek</span></span></p>\n<div>\n<div><u><br /> </u></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>没什么比断网更让人郁闷的事了，不管是断网是因为天气还是没交网费。让我们看看没了网络，我们能用电脑做什么。工作、娱乐。</p>\n<p>虽然我们很多人工作都要用到网络，像我们How-to Geek，但就算断网了，你也可以工作、听音乐、看电影、玩游戏。不能做的只是收发邮件、网上聊天（im、qq）、上社交网站、在线文档、浏览网页。这里我们整理了个建议清单，看看你在断网时可以做什么</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[21-07-34]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[21-07-34]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825210734.png\" width=\"620\" height=\"226\" /></p>\n<h3>进行电脑维护</h3>\n<p>互联网丰富多彩，以至于让你静不下心来，你可能有一段时间没没进行系统维护和<a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/15677/zen-and-the-art-of-file-and-folder-organization/\">文件整理</a>了吧。现在就可以删掉那些不需要的软件了。. 最好的卸载软件及其残留的方法就是用 <a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/reviews/revo-uninstaller-pro/\">Revo Uninstaller Pro</a> 或者 <a href=\"http://blogs.howtogeek.com/mysticgeek/2008/04/29/completely-uninstall-programs-and-more-with-revo-uninstaller/\">Revo Uninstaller Free edition</a>. 希望你已经有安装这软件了。</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-24-47]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-24-47]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100824222447.png\" width=\"427\" height=\"404\" /></p>\n<p>如果你没有安装，那也可以用系统自带的软件卸载程序.只是会卸载会不太干净，会留下写文件夹和注册表垃圾，特别是你卸载的是<a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/23959/completely-remove-itunes-and-other-apple-software-from-a-windows-computer/\">iTunes及其关联</a> </p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-07-10-[22-10-20]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-07-10-[22-10-20]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100710221020.png\" width=\"518\" height=\"397\" /></p>\n<p>你还可以顺便清理下磁盘空间。再次之前最好先保存打开的文档，退出所有的程序。然后在运行对话框中输入%temp%<img title=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-36-17]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-36-17]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100824223617.png\" width=\"438\" height=\"190\" /> </p>\n<p>Ctrl+A 选中所有文件然后删除，就会把磁盘清理程序会漏掉的临时文件夹内容清除了</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-40-49]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-40-49]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100824224049.png\" width=\"583\" height=\"430\" /></p>\n<p>然后清空回收站，运行磁盘清理程序吧</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-44-19]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-44-19]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100824224419.png\" width=\"417\" height=\"504\" /></p>\n<p>也可以使用 <a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/windows-vista/create-a-shortcut-or-hotkey-to-run-ccleaner-silently/\">CCleaner</a>…不管是安装版的还是便携版的。</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[03-58-31]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[03-58-31]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825035831.png\" width=\"632\" height=\"440\" /></p>\n<p>如果你想要清理注册表，那就查找注册表错误，然后点击修复选中错误。你可以让 CCleaner在修复错误前备份注册表。这样当出现问题时以便恢复</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[04-05-34]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[04-05-34]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825040534.png\" width=\"632\" height=\"440\" /></p>\n<p>如果你没设置系统自动整理磁盘碎片，那就趁现在，再弄个定期整理磁盘碎片。在win7开始菜单的搜索框输入disk defrag</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[03-49-56]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[03-49-56]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825034956.png\" width=\"432\" height=\"169\" /></p>\n<p>现在就可以设定整理计划，分析磁盘碎片量，然后运行吧</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[21-37-12]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[21-37-12]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825213712.png\" width=\"619\" height=\"412\" /></p>\n<p>这里有个磁盘整理的例子，更多内容请看 <a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/windows-vista/configure-disk-defragmenter-schedule-in-windows-vista/\">how to configure disk defragmenter in Vista or Windows 7</a>.</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[04-02-21]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[04-02-21]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825040221.png\" width=\"468\" height=\"360\" /></p>\n<p>如果你不喜欢用自带的磁盘整理程序，你可以有别的选择：<a href=\"http://blogs.howtogeek.com/mysticgeek/2007/09/05/defrag-faster-with-auslogics/\">Auslogics Defrag</a>或者 <a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/2363/defraggler-is-a-free-utility-to-defragment-your-hard-drive/\">Defraggler</a>.</p>\n<p><img title=\"defrag2010\" border=\"0\" alt=\"defrag2010\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/defrag2010.png\" width=\"599\" height=\"512\" /></p>\n<h3>清理你真实的桌面和笔记本硬件</h3>\n<p>你桌面上是不是已经积满了灰尘？还是定期清理下吧。搞个电脑清洁套件，清理下机箱里的灰尘吧。也正趁此机会重新插下内存条，检查线路连接、声卡、显卡等等。</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[19-25-49]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[19-25-49]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825192549.png\" width=\"525\" height=\"443\" /></p>\n<p><em>Photo by: </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/pointytilly/2743920595/\"><em>pointytilly</em></a></p>\n<p>你还可以清理下鼠标键盘之类的。如果你最近没清理的话，你会很惊奇键盘里怎么这么多灰尘，食物残渣，猫的毛发。再次请出电脑清洁套件吧。或者，如果你想清理得更彻底，那就把按键一个个撬出来清理吧。</p>\n<p>说到猫，如果你待机状态的电脑老是因为你的爱猫对键盘情有独钟而运行的话，你可以看看此文 <a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/10418/stop-the-mouse-from-waking-up-your-computer-from-sleep-mode/\">stop the mouse or keyboard from waking your computer from Sleep Mode</a>.</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[19-33-30]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[19-33-30]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825193330.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"487\" /></p>\n<p><em>Photo by:  </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/tiger_lily/119747732/\"><em>–Amelie-</em></a></p>\n<h3>工作</h3>\n<p>没网络也可以工作。只要你有本地存档，你就可以接着工作了。</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-58-39]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-58-39]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100824225839.png\" width=\"617\" height=\"584\" /></p>\n<p><strong>整理待办清单和笔记</strong></p>\n<p>你可以不分心第整理你的待办清单和笔记。多亏Evernote 和OneNOte同步的功能，你需要的文档已经在你电脑里了</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-52-32]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-52-32]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100824225232.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"412\" /></p>\n<p>更新待办事务清单。可以用我们之前推荐的免费软件<a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/uncategorized/doomi-is-a-free-small-lightweight-to-do-list-app/\"> Doomi</a>. 它系统资源占用低，方便易用</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[23-13-09]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[23-13-09]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100824231309.png\" width=\"331\" height=\"293\" /></p>\n<p><strong>来场头脑风暴吧</strong></p>\n<p>可以趁这个时间来场头脑风暴：工作项目、网站以及其他你正协同的工作。你可以用其他轻便的软件像：记事本、word、也可以用更复杂的软件像： <a href=\"http://www.actionoutline.com/\">Action Outline</a>.</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[19-46-12]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[19-46-12]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825194612.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"465\" /></p>\n<p><strong>清理收件箱</strong></p>\n<p>虽然不能收发邮件，当你可以清理下收件箱，如果你用的是 Outlook 或Thunderbird邮件客户端的话。删除不需要的邮件，清理已删除邮件，运行自动存档。这样网络回来时，你的邮件就整理好了。</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[23-25-45]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[23-25-45]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100824232545.png\" width=\"573\" height=\"448\" /></p>\n<p>你也可以趁此加速Outlook，请参看 <a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/microsoft-office/make-outlook-faster-by-disabling-unnecessary-add-ins/\">make Outlook faster by disabling unnecessary addins</a>.</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[19-49-25]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[19-49-25]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825194925.png\" width=\"412\" height=\"250\" /></p>\n<p><strong>多多了解你的便携软件</strong></p>\n<p>如果你的U盘装了<a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/19571/disable-the-splash-screen-in-portable-firefox-and-other-portable-apps/\">PortableApps</a> 或者 <a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/17638/fill-a-flash-drive-with-portable-software-using-lupo-pensuite/\">Lupo PenSuite</a>,现在就可以好好探索下你的便携软件了。这样网络恢复后，这些软件用起来就更有效率</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[23-12-44]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[23-12-44]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825231244.png\" width=\"434\" height=\"601\" /></p>\n<h3>娱乐</h3>\n<p>断网后，在等待网络恢复时你还是可以有娱乐活动的。你可以看看硬盘里的媒体文件像 Podcasts, Movies, Music, eBooks…等等</p>\n<p>你可以用Picassa或 <a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/9429/learning-windows-7-manage-photos-with-live-photo-gallery/\">Windows Live Photo Gallery</a>.整理照片</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[22-26-32]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[22-26-32]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825222632.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"565\" /></p>\n<p>如果你订阅了Podcasts, 可能你已经下来些视频片段了。趁此好好再欣赏下吧</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-12-28]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-12-28]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100824221228.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"376\" /></p>\n<p>如果你电脑有电视卡，你可以看电视（不会连有线电视都断了吧）</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-10-28]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-24-[22-10-28]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100824221028.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"370\" /></p>\n<p>当然，你也可以欣赏你下载下来的视频，或者也可以用传统的方式：光盘播放</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[20-51-35]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[20-51-35]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825205135.png\" width=\"627\" height=\"533\" /></p>\n<p><strong>电脑游戏</strong></p>\n<p>很多电脑游戏都有联网，但也有很多单人模式是不需要联网的。<img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[20-59-32]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[20-59-32]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825205932.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"487\" /></p>\n<p> <span>重温下以前的经典老游戏吧<br /> </span> </p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[19-59-34]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[19-59-34]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825195934.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"485\" /></p>\n<p><strong>电子书</strong></p>\n<p>如果你有电脑版的电子阅读器比如KindleIf 或 <a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/26332/read-all-your-ebooks-on-nook-for-pc-and-portable-devices/\">Barnes &#038; Noble’s Nook for PC</a> ，你就可以看看电子书了。</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[20-24-40]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[20-24-40]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825202440.png\" width=\"629\" height=\"512\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/8858/learning-windows-7-manage-your-music-with-windows-media-player/\">整理wmp里的音乐集</a>T或者其他你<a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/24049/ask-the-readers-what-desktop-music-player-do-you-use/\">喜欢的音乐播放器</a> 去除 DRM, c转换音乐格式，用<a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/reviews/tuneclone/\">TuneClone</a>, <a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/reviews/audio-dedupe/\">Audio Dedupe</a>, 查找重复文件 </p>\n<p><img title=\"2010foobar2000organize\" border=\"0\" alt=\"2010foobar2000organize\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/2010foobar2000organize.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"595\" /></p>\n<h3>去免费热点蹭网吧</h3>\n<p>如果你的工作离不开网络，比如上下facebook、搜索最新的Lady Gaga视频,可以带上你的笔记本、上网本、 iOS, or Android设备到有公共热点的地方.嗯，你最好看下<a href=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/26674/keep-your-windows-computer-secure-on-public-wireless-hotspots/\">如何在公共热点保障上网安全</a>。</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[20-30-43]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[20-30-43]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825203043.png\" width=\"566\" height=\"343\" /></p>\n<p><em>Photo by: </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/librarycommission/521630871/\"><em>Nebraska Library Commission</em></a></p>\n<h3>过点电脑以外的生活吧</h3>\n<p>作为奇客，我们大部分的人花太多时间在电脑上，所以是时候休息下了。出门去，散散步，看看书，处理下家务。有时候，远离下充满科技味的一切来清醒头脑很不错。</p>\n<p>有个真实的世界等待我们探索。趁着没网络出去<a href=\"http://productivegeek.com/articles/use-your-geek-skills-to-get-out-there-and-meet-new-people/\">用你的”奇技淫巧“认识新的朋友吧</a>。</p>\n<p><img title=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[20-34-43]\" border=\"0\" alt=\"sshot-2010-08-25-[20-34-43]\" src=\"http://www.howtogeek.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/sshot20100825203443.png\" width=\"452\" height=\"456\" /></p>\n<p><em>Photo by: </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/andrea_rose/2692461897/\"><em>Andrea Rose Marie</em></a></p>\n<p>没有网络，你可以用电脑做什么呢？以上只是些建议。没有网络我们会如何呢，没人知道，但真的事到临头，我们还是有法子的。没网络的生活，你做什么呢？留言评论吧。。</p>\n<div> </div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n<p> </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/90729/131168#newComment\">添加新评论</a></p>\n<p><strong>相关文章：</strong></p>\n<p>  <a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/5974/130669?from=rss_related\">Viral Loop 图书试译 （一）</a></p>\n<p>  <a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/169035/129744?from=rss_related\">试译《边缘女孩》第二章：诱因二  虚幻的网络世界（节选）</a></p>\n<p>  <a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/168786/130971?from=rss_related\">边缘女孩</a></p>\n<p>  <a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/167512/130490?from=rss_related\">Google 最失败的十个产品</a></p>\n<p>  <a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/134499/129886?from=rss_related\">《Viral Loop》图书试译第2页1&#8211;第2页2</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/407924179/yeeyan-tech/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://article.yeeyan.org/view/90729/131168\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/407924179/art01.html\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/yeeyan-tech/407924179/art01.gif\"></a></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/1017243/tongji.gif\" /><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/997968/tongji.gif\" /></p>\n<p>“要翻墙，<a href=\"http://idangxingdafa.info\" target=\"_blank\">用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[19254]}